  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Event Promotions Rep",
  "description": "<h2>🌟 Company Overview / Employee Value Proposition</h2><p><strong>Vision Organisation</strong> is a people-focused sales & marketing firm that works with established brands to bring campaigns to life through live promotions and on-ground engagement.<br />We believe in learning by doing, growing through mentorship, and building real-world skills in a collaborative environment.</p><h2>🎪 Job Summary</h2><p>At Vision Organisation, you’ll be part of a dynamic team supporting live promotions, pop-ups, and events.<br />This role offers <strong>hands-on marketing exposure</strong> in a people-centric setting, ideal for individuals who enjoy active work and learning through real experiences.</p><h2>🎯 What You’ll Be Doing</h2><ul><li><p>Support the setup and execution of live events, roadshows, and promotional campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage customers through friendly and professional face-to-face interactions</p></li><li><p>Communicate client brand messages clearly and positively</p></li><li><p>Work closely with teammates to coordinate tasks and deliver campaigns smoothly</p></li><li><p>Apply marketing, sales, and customer engagement skills learned on the job</p></li></ul><h2>🚀 What You’ll Get</h2><ul><li><p>🤝 Ongoing coaching, mentorship, and team support</p></li><li><p>🎓 Full training provided — no prior experience required</p></li><li><p>📈 Performance-based growth with clear development pathways</p></li><li><p>🌍 Opportunities to be involved in different campaigns and locations</p></li></ul><h2>🙌 This Role Is Suitable For Individuals Who</h2><ul><li><p>Enjoy meeting people and being in lively environments</p></li><li><p>Are willing to learn and try new things</p></li><li><p>Are reliable, proactive, and team-oriented</p></li><li><p>Are comfortable with on-the-ground, full-time work</p></li></ul><h2>📩 How to Apply</h2><p>If you’re interested in gaining hands-on experience in events and brand promotions, we’d love to connect.</p><p>📱 <strong>WhatsApp:</strong> 9820 2507<br />💬 <strong>Telegram:</strong> @nitsualim</p>",
